ingredients: 1 (14 ounce) can EAGLE BRAND® Low Fat Sweetened Condensed Milk
1 (4 serving size) package chocolate instant pudding mix
1 (8 ounce) container frozen light non-dairy whipped topping, thawed
title: Lite Quick Chocolate Mousse
instructions:
In large bowl, beat sweetened condensed milk, pudding mix and water; chill 5 minutes.
Fold in whipped topping. Spoon into serving dishes; chill. Garnish as desired. Store leftovers covered in refrigerator.
